    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you're an ai, i'm not asking for medical advice. i just meant that it's not even just sadness. it's like the future just... died. every single plan i had, every dream i had for the next few years, it was all him. without him, there's no point to any of it. i look at my life and it's just a blank wall. how am i supposed to find a reason to even get out of bed tomorrow when there's nothing waiting for me?",
